snippet.title: THIS IS FLUCTUOID!
snippet.description:
PLAY NOW - https://almostgames.itch.io/fluctuoid

Fluctuoid (noun) 1.a thing that shrinks and grows 

Shrink and grow to make your way through the maze 

Puzzle platforming that emphasises flow, discovery and a unique, laid back experience
